ve the whole thing. Having to navigate to the root part is clunky.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSaaame.\u00A0 It\u0027s just another piece of functionality I\u0027m not quite sure why it isn\u0027t there.\u00A0\u00A0 Surely it can\u0027t be \u003Cstrong\u003Ethat\u003C/strong\u003E complex that it\u0027s gotta be absent on day 1?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}